{"tid":2470242,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃店］亞洲50最佳餐廳「香港大班樓」奪冠！ 美食家叫好","createTime":"2021-03-31T19:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T07:20:08.000Z","uid":212249,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c4ee069c8d9787be8f337ad63667c0a04cc197","tid":2470242,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T19:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2021-03-29/1024/20210329001470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2021-03-29%2F1024%2F20210329001470.jpg&h=0a1621cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大班樓創始人葉一南獲獎「亞洲50最佳餐廳」第一位寶座(圖：港旅局提供)<br />\n<br />\n而此次大贏家可算是香港，大班樓於2009 年開業，以精挑細選的食材及專注於烹調充滿地道風味的粵菜而聞名的，自2013年首次入選以來，一直都是「『亞洲』50最佳餐廳」榜單的常客。而且，大班樓更於2019年首次在「『世界』50最佳餐廳」名單亮相，名列第41位。除了大班樓外，香港新上榜餐廳Mono (第44位)，以及兩間重新上榜的餐廳Caprice (第28位) 和Ta Vie旅 (第38位)。另外，在獨具創意的行政總廚鄭永麒 (Vicky Cheng)領軍下，香港的 Vea (第16位) 成為本年度「待客藝術獎」得主。其餘上榜的香港餐廳包括：Neighborhood (第17位)、Belon (第25位)、8&frac12; Otto e Mezzo Bombana (第33位)、Amber (第37位)、龍景軒 (第47位) 以及家全七福 (第48位)。"},{"pid":"02a7a56d40084133ff7fed92bbd942778c05f78e","tid":2470242,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T19:59:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210329001469-260405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20210329001469-260405&d=6VUJY1vbA2ifZxBcTMZdIwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=60fd3f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210329001469-260405</a>"},{"pid":"ebea0846d6824612ef4f79b35e1cd5ebcbafd7eb","tid":2470242,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T20:10:57.000Z","msg":"貴唔貴？"},{"pid":"8bb4d1405b6ab0fdd6011f9a3f63d955ab2d0390","tid":2470242,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":